Module mesakit.graph.core
Package com.telenav.mesakit.graph

Class Route

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.mesakit.graph.Route
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.string.Stringable, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.string.StringSource, com.telenav.mesakit.map.geography.shape.rectangle.Bounded, Iterable<Edge>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Route.ConcatenatedRoute, Route.OneEdgeRoute
public abstract class Route extends Object implements Iterable<Edge>, com.telenav.mesakit.map.geography.shape.rectangle.Bounded, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.string.Stringable
A list of edges that is organized according to connectivity, forming a continuous route. Attempting to add an Edge to a Route that is not connected to the edges already in the route will result in a run-time exception.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
